description: UR This ONIMATA race is unknown. He's so quiet and stealthy, you can expect him to be anywhere near you whenever you blink your eye. Agility is his top skill. --------------- ONIMATA PROJECT (オニマタ) is my visual storytelling project that felling stories about a group of demons who survived the post apocalyptic world which caused by the unknown organization. ONI means demon in Japanese, and MATA means eye in Bahasa Indonesia.
